# Byte-locked bundles (-text): git must NEVER convert their line endings.
# Their blobs are committed with CRLF on purpose (portable web bundles).
# The previous attribute (text eol=crlf) contradicted the CRLF blobs and
# caused a permanent phantom "modified" state that silently broke pulls
# on every clone.
docs/demo/app/index.html -text
filenymous-app.html -text
